data.description: Hurry before he changes his mind - Seller offering 10K closing credit with approved offer!  Discover unparalleled comfort and elegance at 7220 Duncans Ridge! Nestled on a prime corner lot, this 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home is enveloped by serene views of towering foliage. On the main level, this home has an open layout kitchen, breakfast nook, dining area, laundry room, one bathroom and two bedrooms including the master bedroom. Enjoy cozy nights with endless memories with loved ones by the stunning fireplace that adorns the living room.   On the second level of this home, you will find 2 additional bedrooms each accompanied by 2 full bathrooms.   This Fuquay-Varina gem is in a prime location just minutes away from the downtown area which is home to plenty of shops and restaurants. Immerse yourself in this welcoming community and get a taste for Fuquay' southern hospitality at locally owned establishments including: Aviator Taphouse and Kitchen, Pints Ice Cream, Anna's Pizzeria, Stick Boy Bread Co and Cultivate Coffee.
